            <title>[JCR-2814] Login performance drop when using DefaultAccessManager</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-2814</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-2700&quot; title=&quot;Allow for wildcard restriction in resource-based ACEs&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-2700&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; caused a drop in login performance when using DefaultAccessManager. The drop is caused by the initialization of the LRU map used in CompiledPermissionsImpl. </description>
